AoE armor shred, perma slow, and % health damage

My personal favorite is to build {{item:3710}} and {{item:3074}} on {{champion:33}} before building tankier. First of all, you gain 120 free armor/MR from W, and you gain free AD from the passive, so more attack speed and splash damage/lifesteal just means he's getting more stats for all that defense, since he's getting HP back, doing tons of AoE damage between hydra, ult, and reflect damage, but also still tanking like a monster.

